计算 SHA-256 并返回小写十六进制；低熵敏感字段建议使用 HMAC-SHA256','[{\"name\":\"text\",\"label\":\"字段文本\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"example\":\"abc\"}]','STRING','JAVA',NULL,'com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions','sha256',NULL,1,'2026-07-15 00:41:42','2026-07-15 01:04:54'),(158,0,'GLOBAL','hmacSha256','HMAC-SHA256 字段摘要','使用密钥按 UTF-8 计算 HMAC-SHA256；空密钥返回 null，密钥应从运行时安全变量传入，不要写死在规则中','[{\"name\":\"text\",\"label\":\"字段文本\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"example\":\"abc\"},{\"name\":\"key\",\"label\":\"密钥\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"example\":\"secret-key\"}]','STRING','JAVA',NULL,'com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions','hmacSha256',NULL,1,'2026-07-15 00:41:42','2026-07-15 01:04:54'),(159,0,'GLOBAL','randomInt','随机整数','生成随机整数；支持 randomInt()、randomInt(lower, upper) 和 randomInt(lower, upper, includeLower, includeUpper)，默认闭区间；仅用于普通业务抽样，不用于安全随机','[{\"name\":\"lower\",\"label\":\"下界\",\"type\":\"NUMBER\",\"example\":0},{\"name\":\"upper\",\"label\":\"上界\",\"type\":\"NUMBER\",\"example\":1},{\"name\":\"includeLower\",\"label\":\"包含下界\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"example\":true},{\"name\":\"includeUpper\",\"label\":\"包含上界\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"example\":true}]','NUMBER','JAVA',NULL,'com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.RandomBuiltinFunctions','randomIntForManagement',NULL,1,'2026-07-16 00:08:22','2026-07-16 00:08:22'),(160,0,'GLOBAL','randomDecimal','随机小数','生成随机小数；支持 randomDecimal()、randomDecimal(lower, upper) 和 randomDecimal(lower, upper, includeLower, includeUpper)，默认闭区间；仅用于普通业务抽样，不用于安全随机','[{\"name\":\"lower\",\"label\":\"下界\",\"type\":\"NUMBER\",\"example\":0},{\"name\":\"upper\",\"label\":\"上界\",\"type\":\"NUMBER\",\"example\":1},{\"name\":\"includeLower\",\"label\":\"包含下界\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"example\":true},{\"name\":\"includeUpper\",\"label\":\"包含上界\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"example\":true}]','NUMBER','JAVA',NULL,'com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.RandomBuiltinFunctions','randomDecimalForManagement',NULL,1,'2026-07-16 00:08:22','2026-07-16 00:08:22');
INSERT INTO rule_engine.`rule_function_version` (`id`, `function_id`, `version`, `function_json`, `change_log`, `publish_by`, `publish_time`) VALUES (1,1,1,'{\"createTime\":1783355671000,\"description\":\"身份证提取出生日期\\n\\n参数：idCard（STRING）\\n返回类型：DATE 或 OBJECT\",\"funcCode\":\"idCardBirthDate\",\"funcName\":\"身份证生日提取\",\"id\":1,\"implBeanName\":\"\",\"implClass\":\"\",\"implMethod\":\"\",\"implScript\":\"if (idCard == null) {\\r\\n    return null;\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\nid = idCard.toString().trim();\\r\\n\\r\\nif (id.matches(\\\"^[0-9]{17}[0-9Xx]$\\\")) {\\r\\n    birthText = id.substring(6, 14);\\r\\n} else if (id.matches(\\\"^[0-9]{15}$\\\")) {\\r\\n    birthText = \\\"19\\\" + id.substring(6, 12);\\r\\n} else {\\r\\n    return null;\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\ntry {\\r\\n    formatter = new java.text.SimpleDateFormat(\\\"yyyyMMdd\\\");\\r\\n    formatter.setLenient(false);\\r\\n    return formatter.parse(birthText);\\r\\n} catch (Exception e) {\\r\\n    return null;\\r\\n}\",\"implType\":\"SCRIPT\",\"paramsJson\":\"[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"idCard\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"身份证号\\\"}]\",\"projectId\":0,\"returnType\":\"DATE\",\"scope\":\"GLOBAL\",\"status\":1,\"updateTime\":1783355671000}','create',NULL,'2026-07-07 00:34:31'),(2,162,1,'{\"createTime\":1784047302000,\"description\":\"按 UTF-8 计算 MD5 并返回小写十六进制；仅用于兼容旧系统，不用于密码或安全签名\",\"funcCode\":\"md5\",\"funcName\":\"MD5\",\"id\":162,\"implClass\":\"com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions\",\"implMethod\":\"md5\",\"implType\":\"JAVA\",\"paramsJson\":\"[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"字段文本\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"example\\\":\\\"abc\\\"}]\",\"projectId\":0,\"returnType\":\"STRING\",\"scope\":\"GLOBAL\",\"status\":1,\"updateTime\":1784047302000}','update',NULL,'2026-07-15 00:48:42'),(3,165,1,'{\"createTime\":1784047302000,\"description\":\"使用密钥按 UTF-8 计算 HMAC-SHA256；空密钥返回 null，密钥应从运行时安全变量传入，不要写死在规则中\",\"funcCode\":\"hmacSha256\",\"funcName\":\"HMAC-SHA256\",\"id\":165,\"implClass\":\"com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions\",\"implMethod\":\"hmacSha256\",\"implType\":\"JAVA\",\"paramsJson\":\"[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"字段文本\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"example\\\":\\\"abc\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"key\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"密钥\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"example\\\":\\\"secret-key\\\"}]\",\"projectId\":0,\"returnType\":\"STRING\",\"scope\":\"GLOBAL\",\"status\":1,\"updateTime\":1784047302000}','update',NULL,'2026-07-15 00:49:01'),(4,163,1,'{\"createTime\":1784047302000,\"description\":\"按 UTF-8 计算 SHA-1 并返回小写十六进制；仅用于兼容旧系统，不用于密码或安全签名\",\"funcCode\":\"sha1\",\"funcName\":\"SHA-1\",\"id\":163,\"implClass\":\"com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions\",\"implMethod\":\"sha1\",\"implType\":\"JAVA\",\"paramsJson\":\"[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"字段文本\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"example\\\":\\\"abc\\\"}]\",\"projectId\":0,\"returnType\":\"STRING\",\"scope\":\"GLOBAL\",\"status\":1,\"updateTime\":1784047302000}','update',NULL,'2026-07-15 00:49:08'),(5,164,1,'{\"createTime\":1784047302000,\"description\":\"按 UTF-8 计算 SHA-256 并返回小写十六进制；低熵敏感字段建议使用 HMAC-SHA256\",\"funcCode\":\"sha256\",\"funcName\":\"SHA-256\",\"id\":164,\"implClass\":\"com.hengshucredit.rule.core.function.DigestBuiltinFunctions\",\"implMethod\":\"sha256\",\"implType\":\"JAVA\",\"paramsJson\":\"[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"字段文本\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"STRING\\\",\\\"example\\\":\\\"abc\\\"}]\",\"projectId\":0,\"returnType\":\"STRING\",\"scope\":\"GLOBAL\",\"status\":1,\"updateTime\":1784047302000}','update',NULL,'2026-07-15 00:49:14');
